    Treat the system UI thread as an ExecutorService

    This is done to allow UI codes to be part of UI IThreadType so that IAltFuture objects can be easily defined to execute on the UI thread in Async.UI vs background worker threads.

    Since the system UI thread runs forever, not all ExecutorService items, for example related to lifecycle. make sense to implement.
